            <title>[CASSANDRA-15460] Fix missing call to enable RPC after native transport is started in in-jvm dtests</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/CASSANDRA-15460</link>
                <project id="12310865" key="CASSANDRA">Apache Cassandra</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;When starting the native transport, the original patch missed the step of calling &lt;tt&gt;StorageService.instance.setRpcReady(true);&lt;/tt&gt;. This appears to only be required for counter columns, but without it you can&apos;t update a counter value.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;We should add this call after starting up the native transport, and set it to &lt;tt&gt;false&lt;/tt&gt; during the shutdown sequence to mimic the production code.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
